OL,3,CAfghan man jailed for two years for
OL,4,Cpiloting dinghy in Channel for two
OL,5,Chours
OL,7,FAn Afghan man who steered an
OL,8,Fovercrowded dinghy in the Channel for
OL,9,Ftwo hours has been jailed for two
OL,10,Fyears for endangering others.
OL,12,FBasir Ramatullah, also known as Baseer
OL,13,FAhmad, was sentenced at Canterbury
OL,14,FCrown Court, after pleading guilty to
OL,15,Fendangering others during a sea
OL,16,Fcrossing on May 2.
OL,18,FThe court heard the 21-year-old
OL,19,Ftravelled along with 53 other migrants
OL,20,Fon an overcrowded inflatable boat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
