PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784839668
OL,3,CAfghan man jailed for two years for
OL,4,Cpiloting dinghy in Channel for two
OL,5,Chours
OL,7,FSurveillance imagery found Ramatullah
OL,8,Fto be in control of the boat for more
OL,9,Fthan two hours, prosecutor Ben Wild
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Prior to the boat being stopped by
OL,13,FBorder Force, Mr Ahmad was seen to
OL,14,Fmove away from the engine and sit on
OL,15,Fthe floor," he added.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@KO]
