FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784839668
OL,3,CAfghan man jailed for two years for
OL,4,Cpiloting dinghy in Channel for two
OL,5,Chours
OL,7,FSentencing him, Judge Edmund Fowler
OL,8,Fsaid: "You were identified as having
OL,9,Fendangered others, because you had
OL,10,Fbeen observed being in control of the
OL,11,Fvessel for some two hours crossing the
OL,12,FEnglish Channel in an extremely busy
OL,13,Fstretch of water.
OL,15,F"The rib was overloaded, at least one
OL,16,Fperson was not wearing a personal
OL,17,Fflotation device.
OL,19,F"As a Border Force vessel approached
OL,20,Fyou, you moved away from the engine
OL,21,Fand sat on the floor."
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU{D@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
