OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784839668
OL,3,CAfghan man jailed for two years for
OL,4,Cpiloting dinghy in Channel for two
OL,5,Chours
OL,7,FShe told the court "it was not a
OL,8,Fchoice" to pilot the boat, but he took
OL,9,Fthe role after a human trafficker
OL,10,Fsteering it jumped off the vessel, and
OL,11,Fthe trafficker's companion "gave up"
OL,12,Fsteering.
OL,14,F"Nobody else (was) willing to handle
OL,15,Fthe boat and that is why he then took
OL,16,Fcharge piloting the boat," the lawyer
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FThe Afghan national had no previous
OL,20,Fconvictions or previous immigration
OL,21,Fhistory in the UK.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@GO]sD@\OUsD@dO]vD@AOUxD@ZO]
